{"tid":1003121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知名度超高！麥當勞唐氏症暖男工作32年退休　顧客讚：他永遠掛著微笑","createTime":"2019-01-31T11:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T13:23:53.000Z","uid":212399,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4ccaf22a3b8f55534a1e82de4c6f9cb57e9d8f","tid":1003121,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2018/12/15/09/7457230-0-image-a-12_1544867573485.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2018%2F12%2F15%2F09%2F7457230-0-image-a-12_1544867573485.jpg&h=9d214d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 奧格雷迪對工作投入的程度，就連家人都感到相當自豪。<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n澳洲雪梨一間麥當勞有位特別鼓舞人心、臉上堆滿笑容的員工，那就是服務長達32年、罹患唐氏症的奧格雷迪（Russell O&rsquo;grady），因為當他從18歲穿上麥當勞制服的那一天開始，他招呼客人、擦拭桌面的身影令人印象深刻，被封為當地最有名的人。如今50歲的他宣告退休。<br />\n每日郵報報導，奧格雷迪當年出社會的年代，只有少數身障人士能找得到工作，在他進入麥當勞上班後，就再也沒有轉換過工作跑道，不但非常熱愛這份工作，更給了他不同的人生觀。奧格雷迪的父親傑夫（Geoff O'Grady）提到，「曾經有人問他，『請問你是殘疾人士嗎？』，而他當時回答，『我以前上學的時候是，但我現在在麥當勞上班』。」<br />\n奧格雷迪的父親提到，奧格雷迪溫柔親切，也非常受人愛戴和欣賞，人們甚至會在街頭和他握手，「到那種我們都不敢置信的地步。」但如今的奧格雷迪為了身體健康狀況，宣告退休。<br />\n麥當勞主管珀賽爾（Courtney Purcell）表示，奧格雷迪在當地的知名度相當高，甚至有老客戶會專門在禮拜四或禮拜五的時候過來看他，「我們會想念他的」。<br />\n在奧格雷迪退休的消息傳出後，一名網友留言提到，「親愛的奧格雷迪，我記得你，總是微笑，而且在情況允許的時候，隨時準備好幫助他人&hellip;祝福你在下個生命階段旅程一切順利。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181216/1332240.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181216%2F1332240.htm&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=55f24fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181216/1332240.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b620e352f412a6e8444a165e7fbff91fb4db1201","tid":1003121,"uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20141204/640_ee3acfd9c21863ed3c773f756e4b5ee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20141204%2F640_ee3acfd9c21863ed3c773f756e4b5ee6.jpg&h=034a0a6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c13ee7af28f2779b3e05244801e40a351e7abdc5","tid":1003121,"uid":34023,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"b620e352f412a6e8444a165e7fbff91fb4db1201","tid":1003121,"uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20141204/640_ee3acfd9c21863ed3c773f756e4b5ee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20141204%2F640_ee3acfd9c21863ed3c773f756e4b5ee6.jpg&h=034a0a6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"弱智嘅都嚇到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c733228a6ab901b730202952bbbace79888464d2","tid":1003121,"uid":162485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:02:32.000Z","msg":"麥當勞 hall of fame"},{"pid":"5081a92a47361e65ba914a08ffb68339c146c3e5","tid":1003121,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"溝唔溝到女？"},{"pid":"fcc2ac25a316f7ce8b6dc26c326032af0f89f63c","tid":1003121,"uid":196329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"麥當勞係咪咁唔負責任？當員工係咩？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cibFFS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cibFFS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b659c426734e702b96029fc366dbd5db3cf606fb","tid":1003121,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c13ee7af28f2779b3e05244801e40a351e7abdc5","tid":1003121,"uid":34023,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"b620e352f412a6e8444a165